==意義及翻譯==
性（sexuality）在中文界中沒統一的翻譯，部分譯者會把其譯為性存在、性现象、性态等等，而[[潘绥铭|潘绥铭]]及黄盈盈於《性社会学》中指出，目前的共識仍是沿用「性」這個字，不過背後的意義會有所改變；著者們則推薦把sexuality翻譯為「全性」<ref name="性社会学">{{cite book|title=性社会学|author1=潘绥铭|author2=黄盈盈|publisher=中国人民大学出版社|year=2011|isbn=9787300133171}}</ref>{{rp|37-38}}。

性（sex）為一個較為強調生物特征和行为学意義的用語；性（sexuality）則較為強調[[社会学|社会学]]与[[心理学|心理学]]上的性。[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]於2001年把前者定義為「决定人类男女两性的性象谱的生物特征的总和」；後者的定義則為「包括性（sex）、性别、[[性别认同|性别认同]]与[[性向认同|性向认同]]、[[性取向|性取向]]、性爱倾向、情感依恋/情欲和生殖的人的核心方面。它以思想、幻想、欲望、信仰、态度、价值、行为、习惯、角色和关系予以体验或表达。性是生物的、心理的、社会经济的、文化上的、伦理上的和宗教上/精神上的诸因素相互影响的结果。」<ref name="性社会学"/>{{rp|37-38}}<ref>{{cite web|author1=世界卫生组织|author2=世界性学会|display-authors=etal|others=彭晓辉译|title=性健康促进行动方案：区域磋商会议纪要|year=2006|url=http://www2.hu-berlin.de/sexology/CH/PSHC/PSH-CH/02cf.html|accessdate=2019-06-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100607221256/http://www2.hu-berlin.de/sexology/CH/PSHC/PSH-CH/02cf.html|archivedate=2010-06-07}}</ref>

== 發展 ==
=== 先天與后天 ===
性被認為是人類與生俱來的；這些特性可能會被人與人交往的物質和社會環境所改變。人類的性是由遺傳和心理活動驅動的。性衝動會影響個人身份和社會活動的發展<ref name="Il posto dell'amore negato"> {{Cite book |author = Leonardo Boccadoro, Sabina Carulli |title = Il posto dell'amore negato. Sessualità e psicopatologie segrete |publisher = Leonardo Boccadoro |date = 2008 |ISBN = 9788895554037 |accessdate = 2017-07-26}} </ref><ref> {{Cite book |author = Gilles Deleuze, Félix Guattari |title = [[反俄狄浦斯|Anti-Oedipus]] |location = France |publisher = Les Éditions de Minuit |date = 1972 |pages = 322 |ISBN = 2707300675 |accessdate = 2017-07-26}} </ref>。一個人的規範性、社會性、文化性、教育性和環境性特徵緩和了性衝動<ref name="Il posto dell'amore negato"/>。

兩個著名的心理學學派在「先天與后天」的辯論中採取了正反立場，分別是由[[西格蒙德·佛洛伊德|西格蒙德·佛洛伊德]]領導的[[精神分析學|精神分析學派]]及其起源能追溯至[[約翰·洛克|約翰·洛克]]的[[行為主義|行為主義學派]]。佛洛伊德相信性衝動是人類的本能。他表示人類有很多本能，但這些本能能大致分為兩大類：[[厄洛斯|厄洛斯]]（生命本能，包括自我保護和色情本能）及[[桑納托斯|桑納托斯]]（死亡本能，包括侵略、自我毀滅和殘酷的本能）<ref name="BarbaraGalle">{{cite journal |author= Barbara Galle |date= 2005 |title= Sylvia Plath - a woman between Eros and Thanatos |journal= Acta neophilologica |volume= 38 |issue= 1 |pages= 97-112 |access-date= 2017-07-26}}</ref>。佛洛伊德的本能理論指出人類從出生開始便被慾望驅使，渴望獲得和增強身體上的快感，因而他支持先天因素。佛洛伊德更重新界定了性欲，使其涵蓋從人體衍生出來的任何形式的快樂<ref name="BarbaraGalle"/>。另一方面，洛克的思想理論則被視為[[白板_(哲學)|白板]]，並在後來被行為主義者用來支持周遭環境是人類逐漸發展自己的性的觀點<ref> {{Cite book | author = William C. Crain | title = Theories of Development: Concepts and Applications | url = https://archive.org/details/theoriesofdevelo00crai_0 |edition = Fourth Edition | location = Englewood Cliffs, N.J. | publisher = Prentice-Hall | date = 2000 | ISBN = 9780139554025 | accessdate = 2017-07-26 | language = en}} </ref>。

===性別差異===
研究者已經提出了心理學上的理論，以解釋在人類的性上所出現的性別差異。精神分析學理論、[[社會生物學|社會生物學]]理論、{{link-en|社會學習理論|Social learning theory}}、{{link-en|角色理論|Role theory|社會角色理論}}、[[腳本理論|腳本理論]]皆認為，社會會較傾向接受男性性滥交（在一段穩定關係以外跟外人發生性關係、擁有多個性伴侶）。該些理論與有關美國男女對性滥交的態度的研究相符；而性滿意度、對[[自慰|自慰]]和[[同性戀|同性戀]]的態度、[[口交|口交]]的盛行率等調查項目則只有很少差異。兩性的性伴侶數量存有「中等程度」的差異——男性的性伴侶一般稍多於女性<ref name="Oliver & Hyde">{{cite book |last1=Oliver |first1=Mary Beth |last2=Hyde |first2=Janet S. |editor1-last=Baumeister |editor1-first=Roy F. |title=Social Psychology and Human Sexuality: Essential Readings |date=2001 |publisher=Psychology Press |isbn=978-1-84169-019-3 |pages=29–43 |chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=2qsKNaqIsuUC&pg=PA29 |language=en |chapter=Gender Differences in Sexuality: A Meta-Analysis |access-date=2019-06-20 |archive-date=2020-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200524102421/https://books.google.com/books?id=2qsKNaqIsuUC&pg=PA29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==生物學層面==
人類就像其他靈長類動物一樣，可大致分為男女兩大性別<ref name="Leonard2010">{{cite book | last =Leonard | first =Janet | title =The Evolution of Primary Sexual Characters in Animals | publisher =Oxford University Press | date =18 Jun 2010 | page =552 | url ={{Google books |plainurl=yes |id=PgtXj5R6OfMC }} | isbn =978-0-19-532555-3 }}</ref>。除此之外也有一部分是[[雙性人|雙性人]]，他們的各項身體特徵「不能夠符合傳統上男女身體的定義」<ref name="un-2016">{{Citation | last1 = UN Committee against Torture | last2 = UN Committee on the Rights of the Child | last3 = UN Committee on the Rights of People with Disabilities | last4 = UN Subcommittee on Prevention of Torture and other Cruel, Inhuman or Degrading Treatment or Punishment | last5 = Juan Méndez | last6 = Dainius Pῡras | last7 = Dubravka Šimonoviæ | last8 = Marta Santos Pais | last9 = African Commission on Human and Peoples' Rights | last10 = Council of Europe Commissioner for Human Rights | last11 = Inter-American Commission on Human Rights | work = Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights | title = Intersex Awareness Day – Wednesday 26 October. End violence and harmful medical practices on intersex children and adults, UN and regional experts urge | date = 24 October 2016 | url = http://www.ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/DisplayNews.aspx?NewsID=20739&LangID=E | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161121185256/http://ohchr.org/EN/NewsEvents/Pages/DisplayNews.aspx?NewsID=20739&LangID=E | archivedate = 2016-11-21 | accessdate = 2019-06-20 }}</ref>，約0.018%至1.7%的新生兒為雙性人<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.intersexequality.com/how-common-is-intersex-in-humans/ |title=How Common is Intersex? An Explanation of the Stats. |publisher=[[Intersex_Campaign_for_Equality|Intersex Campaign for Equality]] |date=2015-04-01 |access-date=2021-01-01 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211235549/https://www.intersexequality.com/how-common-is-intersex-in-humans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://ihra.org.au/16601/intersex-numbers/ |title=Intersex population figures |publisher=Intersex Human Rights Australia |date=2013-09-28 |access-date=2021-01-01 |archive-date=2018-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717183724/https://ihra.org.au/16601/intersex-numbers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=sax>{{cite journal |last1=Sax |first1=Leonard |title=How common is intersex? a response to Anne Fausto-Sterling |journal=Journal of Sex Research |date=2002 |volume=39 |issue=3 |pages=174–178 |doi=10.1080/00224490209552139 |pmid=12476264 |url=https://www.leonardsax.com/how-common-is-intersex-a-response-to-anne-fausto-sterling/ |issn=0022-4499 |access-date=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228000512/https://www.leonardsax.com/how-common-is-intersex-a-response-to-anne-fausto-sterling/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。性生物學的範圍涵蓋了人的生殖系統、[[人类性反应周期|人类性反应周期]]、影響上述兩者的因子。此外其也涵蓋會影響性的其他層面的因子，包括器質性和神經性反應<ref>Ellen Ross, Rayna Rapp Sex and Society: A Research Note from Social History and Anthropology Comparative Studies in Society and History, Vol. 23, No. 1 (Jan. 1981), pp. 51–72</ref>、遺傳、激素問題、性別問題、性功能障礙<ref name="Rathus, Spencer A. 2014">{{cite book | last1= Rathus |first1=Spencer A. |last2=Nevid |first2=Jeffrey S |last3=Fichner-Rathus |first3=Lois | year = 2014| title = Human Sexuality in a World of Diversity | edition =9th | location =  | publisher = Allyn & Bacon | pages = | url =  | access-date =  | quote =  }}</ref>{{rp|4、155}}。
===解剖與生殖===
男女的解剖結構差異在早至胎兒期就已出現，而當中差異仍會隨著發育而擴闊<ref name="人类的性存在">{{Cite book|author1=珍妮特·S·海德|author2=約翰·D·德拉馬特|title=人类的性存在|url=https://archive.org/details/renleidexingcunz0008hyde|publisher=上海社會科学院出版社|year=2005|isbn=7-80681-730-1}}</ref>{{rp|108}}。一般青少男在成年之前便具有生育能力<ref name="Steinberg, L. 2008">Steinberg, L. (2008). ''Adolescence''. New York, NY: McGraw-Hill.</ref>；而女性在初潮後再過幾年才具有完全的生育能力，因為常规性排卵在初潮大约兩年后才会出现<ref>Hafetz, E. (1976). Parameters of sexual maturity in man. In E. Hafetz (Ed.), ''Perspectives in human reproduction'', Vol. 3: ''Sexual maturity: Physiological and clinical parameters.'' Ann Arbor, MI: Ann Arbor Science Publishers.</ref>。在[[麥斯特與強生|麥斯特與強生]]的研究中，儘管兩性面對性刺激時的反應存有一些細微的差異，但基本類似<ref name="Archer, Lloyd">{{cite book| authors = John Archer, Barbara Lloyd| title = Sex and Gender| publisher = Cambridge University Press| year = 2002| pages = 85–88| accessdate = August 25, 2012| isbn = 0521635330| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=BJ1V9r_J0sUC&pg=PA85| archive-date = 2016-05-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160501094829/https://books.google.com/books?id=BJ1V9r_J0sUC&pg=PA85| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Masters & Johnson">Masters & Johnson ''Human Sexual Response'', Bantam, 1981{{ISBN|978-0-553-20429-2}}; 1st ed. 1966</ref>。女性的生殖週期以約28日的方式循環，大多數成年男性的精子會不斷地生成<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|97、133}}。
====腦部====
邊緣系統及其附近區域對性反應的控制發揮了關鍵作用<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|256}}，其會使男性出現[[勃起|心因性勃起]]<ref name="Перехов">{{cite web| url = http://ps-narc-dept.16mb.com/pdf/per/1p.pdf| title = Психогенная эректильная дисфункция| author = Перехов, Алексей Яковлевич| publisher = Клинический опыт| accessdate = 2012-09-17| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6BS3zI7GS?url=http://ps-narc-dept.16mb.com/pdf/per/1p.pdf| archivedate = 2012-10-16| dead-url = yes}}</ref>，兼在[[性高潮|高潮]]时出現明顯的變化<ref name="health.discovery.com">{{cite web |title=Orgasm |publisher=Health.discovery.com |accessdate=2010-04-21 |url=http://science.howstuffworks.com/life/human-biology/orgasm.htm |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403181734/http://health.howstuffworks.com/sexual-health/sexuality/orgasm.htm |archivedate=2016-04-03 }}</ref>。

[[催产素|催产素]]、[[催乳素|催乳素]]、[[促卵泡激素|促卵泡激素]]、[[黄体生成素|黄体生成素]]皆在人類的性上扮演一定角色。催产素和催乳素皆會刺激育後女性分泌乳汁，且會在兩性的高潮期間釋放，帶來緩和放鬆感<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Exton MS, Krüger TH, Koch M, ''et al.'' |title=Coitus-induced orgasm stimulates prolactin secretion in healthy subjects |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_psychoneuroendocrinology_2001-04_26_3/page/287 |journal=Psychoneuroendocrinology |volume=26 |issue=3 |pages=287–94 |date=2001-04 |pmid=11166491 |doi=10.1016/S0306-4530(00)00053-6}}</ref><ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|111}}。促卵泡激素是女性排卵的根本原因，因其會促使卵細胞成熟；其在男性中則掌控精子的產生<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|109、131}}。黄体生成素和促卵泡激素的水平波動最終會誘發排卵<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|131}}。

====男性性器官====
{{main|男性生殖系統}}
男性性器官可分為內外兩部，其對性愛與生殖有著重要作用<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|93、96}}。精子的生产跟女性一樣，也是周期性的，不過精子生产周期達每天上千萬乃至數億條<ref name="ReferenceA"/>{{rp|32}}。
=====外生殖器=====
[[File:Penis(Asia).jpg|thumb]]
男性的外生殖器由[[人類陰莖|陰莖]]及[[陰囊|陰囊]]所組成。精液及尿液皆會在陰莖末端（[[龜頭|龜頭]]）排出<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|93-96}}。一項量度了15,521名男性的陰莖尺寸的研究顯示，陰莖勃起時的平均長度為13.12厘米，平均周徑為11.66厘米<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.realclearscience.com/journal_club/2015/03/03/is_your_penis_normal_theres_a_chart_for_that_109106.html|title=Is Your Penis Normal? There's a Chart for That - RealClearScience|publisher=|accessdate=2019-06-22|archive-date=2015-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150304034207/https://www.realclearscience.com/journal_club/2015/03/03/is_your_penis_normal_theres_a_chart_for_that_109106.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。 陰莖可分為三個部分：陰莖體、陰莖根部、陰莖頭<ref>{{cite book|last1=Crooks|first1=Robert L|last2=Baur|first2=Karla|isbn=978-0-495-81294-4|title=Our Sexuality|page=88|year=2011|publisher=Cengage learning|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&pg=PA88|access-date=2019-06-22|archive-date=2020-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200524102457/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&pg=PA88|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

陰莖體內含三個長筒狀的海綿體組織，兩個並排於上方的為陰莖海綿體，在底的為尿道海綿體；後者在末端擴大，形成陰莖尖端<ref name="ReferenceB">{{cite web |url=http://www.innerbody.com/image/repmov.html |title=Male Reproductive System – Explore Anatomy with Detailed Pictures |publisher=Innerbody.com |accessdate=2013-06-30 |archive-date=2020-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214230107/https://www.innerbody.com/image/repmov.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|93-94}}。海綿體組織內存有空腔，在[[勃起|勃起]]時會充血<ref name="goodarticle">{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.hawaii.edu/hivandaids/Physiology_of_Penile_Erection_and_Pathophysiology_of_Erectile_Dysfunction.pdf
 |title       = Physiology of Penile Erection and Pathophysiology of Erectile Dysfunction
 |author      = Robert C. Dean, Tom F. Lue
 |date        = 2005-11-01
 |work        = NIH-PA Author Manuscript
 |publisher   = Национальные институты здравоохранения США
 |accessdate  = 2012-10-17
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/6BYhVr870?url=http://www.hawaii.edu/hivandaids/Physiology_of_Penile_Erection_and_Pathophysiology_of_Erectile_Dysfunction.pdf
 |archivedate = 2012-10-20
 |dead-url    = yes
}}</ref>。龜頭與陰莖體以冠狀脊為分界<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|93}}。陰莖體的底部分叉成二個陰莖腳，跟恥骨相連<ref>{{cite book|author1=W.馬斯特斯|author2=V.約翰遜|year=1989|publisher   = 知識出版社 |others=馬曉年、賈孟春、王介東、於和鳴等譯|title=人类性反应|page=171|isbn=7-5015-0326-5}}</ref>。圍繞著根部的坐骨海綿體肌和球海綿體肌有助於當事人勃起和射精<ref name=Marieb>{{cite book | last = Marieb | first = Elaine | title = Anatomy & physiology | publisher = Benjamin-Cummings | location =  | page= 895 | year = 2013 | isbn = 9780321887603 }}</ref>。

龜頭之上由可以縮回的包皮所覆蓋，不過其可能因文化、宗教或醫學因素而被[[包皮環切術|切割掉]]<ref name=WHO_2007_GTDPSA>{{cite web |title=Male circumcision: Global trends and determinants of prevalence, safety and acceptability |year=2007 |publisher=World Health Organization |url=http://www.unaids.org/sites/default/files/media_asset/jc1360_male_circumcision_en_0.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2019-06-22 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222194858/http://www.unaids.org/sites/default/files/media_asset/jc1360_male_circumcision_en_0.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=lissauer_2012>{{cite book |author=Lissauer T, Clayden G |title=Illustrated Textbook of Paediatrics, Fourth edition |pages=352–353 |date=October 2011 |publisher=Elsevier |isbn=978-0-7234-3565-5}}</ref><ref name=hay_2012>{{cite book |author=Hay W, Levin M |title=Current Diagnosis and Treatment Pediatrics 21/E |pages=18–19 |date=25 June 2012 |publisher=McGraw Hill Professional |isbn=978-0-07-177971-5 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=V8lMJniWK_QC |access-date=2019-06-22 |archive-date=2020-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729134007/https://books.google.com/books?id=V8lMJniWK_QC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在陰囊以內的睾丸可因溫度或情緒而貼近/遠離身體，這能避免精子受損<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|96-97}}<ref>{{cite news|last1=Drew|first1=Liam|title=The Scrotum Is Nuts|url=http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/science/2013/07/are_testicles_external_for_cooling_galloping_display_or_something_else.1.html|accessdate=3 July 2015|publisher=Slate|date=8 July 2013|archive-date=2017-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602205148/http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/science/2013/07/are_testicles_external_for_cooling_galloping_display_or_something_else.1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Madaras|first1=Lynda Madaras with Area|title=The what's happening to my body? book for boys|date=2008|publisher=Newmarket|location=New York|isbn=978-1-55704-765-6|edition=Rev.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zC1g5gdJc_kC&pg=PA33|accessdate=3 July 2015|archive-date=2020-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200524102532/https://books.google.com/books?id=zC1g5gdJc_kC&pg=PA33|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=====內生殖器=====
[[File:Male_anatomy_zh.svg|thumb]]
男性的內生殖器包括睾丸、前列腺、[[尿道球腺|尿道球腺]]、輸精管<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|96-98}}。

[[睾丸|睾丸]]是男性的性腺，其會製造[[精子|精子]]及[[睾酮|睾酮]]。精子的生成由其生精管負責。{{link-en|間質細胞|Leydig cell}}則負責生成睾酮<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|96-97}}。[[精索|精索]]為睾丸的血液供應源，其包含血管、神经、输精管，而它的肌肉能夠使睾丸跟身體的距離随温度变化和性兴奋程度而改變<ref>{{cite book|editor1=Richard D. McAnulty|editor2=M. Michele Burnette|title=Sex and Sexuality: Sexual function and dysfunction|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=mspeVrvH2QoC&pg=PA15|year=2006|publisher=Greenwood|page=15|isbn=0-275-98581-4|access-date=2019-06-22|archive-date=2020-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200524102537/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=mspeVrvH2QoC&pg=PA15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ReferenceA"/>{{rp|32}}。

精子在射出之前會先經過四個部分。精子在生成後會先進入[[附睾|附睾]]內等待成熟。睾丸內有生精小管，即盘绕在每个睾丸顶部和后部的通道。之後其在射精前會進入始于附睾下端的[[输精管|输精管]]，输精管沿睾丸端向上，成為精索的一部分<ref name="ReferenceB"/>，扩张的一端是壶腹。然後再進入沿經[[前列腺|前列腺]]並延伸到[[尿道|尿道]]的[[射精管|射精管]]，與[[前列腺液|前列腺液]]混合，在尿道射出<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|97}}。前列腺是一个实心的栗子形器官，它围绕着尿道的第一部分，並儲存着前列腺液<ref name="ReferenceA"/>{{rp|33}}<ref name="ReferenceB"/>。其如同女性的[[G點|G點]]，一樣能在[[肛交|肛交]]時提供快感，以至達至[[性高潮|性高潮]]<ref name="Rosenthal">{{cite book |first=Martha |last=Rosenthal |title=Human Sexuality: From Cells to Society |publisher=Cengage Learning |year=2012 |pages=133–135 |isbn=978-0-618-75571-4 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT153 |access-date=2019-06-22 |archive-date=2016-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520211405/https://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT153 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

前列腺和精囊产生的液體，在与精子混合后，統稱為精液<ref name="ReferenceA"/>{{rp|33}}。前列腺位於直腸前、膀胱之下。它由兩個主要區域組成：內部區域能夠產生分泌物，潤滑男性尿道內壁；外部區域則能產生前列腺液，使精液更易離開<ref name="ReferenceB"/>。

