===法律問題===
{{Main|家庭法|离婚|婚姻|人类性行为#限制與規範|性與法律}}
世界各地皆以法律規限人類的性，比如把某些性行為刑事化、給予個體作出性相關抉擇的[[自主權|自主權]]或私隱、使人們得到平等對待，免受歧視；就婚姻和家庭问题进行立法；保护个人免受暴力、骚扰、迫害<ref name=SexualityLaw1>{{cite web |last1=Mills |first1=Elizabeth |last2=Haste |first2=Polly |last3=Wood |first3=Stephen |date=2016-06-17 |title=1. Issues and Debates; How is sexuality regulated in law? |work=Sexuality and Social Justice: A Toolkit |publisher=Institute of Development Studies, Sexuality, Poverty and Law Programme |url=http://www.spl.ids.ac.uk/sexuality-and-social-justice-toolkit/1-issues-and-debates/how-sexuality-regulated-law |access-date=2016-06-17 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204103147/http://www.spl.ids.ac.uk/sexuality-and-social-justice-toolkit/1-issues-and-debates/how-sexuality-regulated-law |dead-url=no }}</ref>。人類的性法律最早可追溯至大約公元前2100年的[[乌尔纳姆法典|烏爾納姆王朝]]，當中包含了對[[通姦|通姦]]的處罰<ref>{{cite book|title=性审判史 一部人类文明史|pages=10-11|year=2015|isbn=978-7-305-14507-0|publisher =南京大學出版社|author=埃里克·伯科威茨|others=王一多、朱洪濤譯}}</ref>。

很多國家都會就[[強奸|強奸]]、[[性侵犯|性侵犯]]<ref name="Sex and Society">{{cite book | author = Marshall Cavendish Corporation | title = Sex and Society | publisher = Marshall Cavendish Corporation | year = 2010 | pages = 143–144 | accessdate = 2013-08-25 | isbn = 0-7614-7906-6 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=aVDZchwkIMEC&lpg=PA143 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143600/http://books.google.com/books?id=aVDZchwkIMEC&lpg=PA143 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Greenberg2">{{cite book|author=Jerrold S. Greenberg|author2=Clint E. Bruess|author3=Sarah C. Conklin|title=Exploring the Dimensions of Human Sexuality|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|year=2010|page=515|accessdate=2013-08-25|isbn=0-7637-7660-2|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1NC5R0RozBYC&lpg=PA515|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143555/http://books.google.com/books?id=1NC5R0RozBYC&lpg=PA515|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[近亲性行为相关的法律|近亲性行为]]<ref name="Bittles">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=t6CsCXXE8skC&pg=PA178|title=Consanguinity in Context|last=Bittles|first=Alan Holland|publisher=Cambridge University Press|year=2012|isbn=0521781868|pages=178–187|accessdate=2013-08-27|archive-date=2020-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518225404/https://books.google.com/books?id=t6CsCXXE8skC&pg=PA178|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[最低合法性行為年齡|最低合法性行為年齡]]<ref name="Kinnear">{{cite book | author = Karen L. Kinnear | title = Childhood Sexual Abuse: A Reference Handbook | publisher = ABC-CLIO | year = 2007 | page = 89 | accessdate = 2013-08-25 | isbn = 1-85109-905-0 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=V1rogCrcOMwC&printsec=frontcover&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9iFlUqmkE4e_2QX_84GgBA&ved=0CEoQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=&f=false | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231223642/http://books.google.com/books?id=V1rogCrcOMwC&printsec=frontcover&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9iFlUqmkE4e_2QX_84GgBA&ved=0CEoQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=&f=false | archive-d